---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of use for No Lock-In Printer, including informational content, affiliate links, and purchase responsibility."
>
  <article class="article">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--amber);">Terms</p>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      By using No Lock-In Printer, you agree that the site is provided for informational research and buying guidance.
    </p>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>No professional advice</h2>
      <p>
        The site provides independent research notes, not professional technical, legal, or financial advice. Product details can change, and you are responsible for confirming compatibility, warranty terms, and purchase conditions before buying.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        We link to official sources, retailers, media coverage, and other third-party websites. We are not responsible for their content, pricing, policies, or availability.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        We aim to keep pages useful and current, but we do not guarantee that every printer price, model variant, driver package, or firmware behavior is accurate at the moment you read it.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
